## 2. 🔄 Flow Design

### 1. Registration & Phone Verification Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as MFE Shell UI
    participant Auth as UserService (.NET)
    participant SMS as SMS/Email Provider
    
    UI->>Auth: 1. Gửi thông tin (Name, Email, Phone, Pass, Confirm Pass)
    Auth->>Auth: 2. Validate dữ liệu & Lưu User dạng "Pending/Unverified"
    Auth->>SMS: 3. Generate OTP & Yêu cầu gửi SMS/Email
    SMS->>UI: 4. Nhận mã OTP qua điện thoại
    UI->>Auth: 5. Nhập OTP & Submit /api/auth/verify-otp
    Auth->>Auth: 6. Check OTP hợp lệ -> Set PhoneNumberVerified = true
    Auth->>UI: 7. Xác nhận Đăng ký thành công
```

### 2. Login Flow (Bằng Email hoặc Số điện thoại)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as MFE Shell UI
    participant BFF as Next.js API/BFF
    participant Auth as UserService (.NET)
    
    UI->>BFF: 1. Gửi (Email hoặc Phone) & Password
    BFF->>Auth: 2. Proxy request /api/auth/login
    Auth->>Auth: 3. Kiểm tra (Email OR Phone) & Verify BCrypt Hash
    Auth->>BFF: 4. Trả về Access Token + Refresh Token
    BFF->>UI: 5. Set-Cookie: 
               AccessToken (HttpOnly, Secure, SameSite) 
               RefreshToken (HttpOnly, Secure)
               & Return Role/User Meta
```

### 3. Forgot Password Flow
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as MFE Shell UI
    participant Auth as UserService (.NET)
    participant SMS as SMS/Email Provider
    
    UI->>Auth: 1. Yêu cầu reset pass (Gửi Email hoặc Phone)
    Auth->>SMS: 2. Generate OTP & Gửi mã cho user
    SMS->>UI: 3. User nhận mã OTP
    UI->>Auth: 4. Submit OTP + Password Mới
    Auth->>Auth: 5. Validate OTP -> Update PasswordHash mới
    Auth->>UI: 6. Đổi mật khẩu thành công
```

### Authenticated Request Flow (Sau login)
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant MFE as Micro-Frontend
    participant GW as ApiGateway (.NET)
    participant Post as PostService (.NET)
    
    MFE->>GW: 1. Gọi /api/posts (Trình duyệt tự đính kèm Cookie)
    GW->>GW: 2. [Middleware] Trích xuất JWT từ Cookie / Header
    GW->>GW: 3. Validate Token Signature & Expiry
    GW->>Post: 4. Forward request (kèm UserId trong header)
    Post->>Post: 5. Authorize/Do Logic
    Post->>MFE: 6. Response Data
```

